	text		"#str_380139"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_20_10_1
{
	description	"Private Strauss, it looks like Corporal Kane has arrived."
	text		"#str_380140"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_20_60_1
{
	description	"This is Falcon 6 making a run on the Networking Tower. Anti-aircraft is heavy."
	text		"#str_380141"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_20_60_2
{
	description	"I'm hit! Energizers are off line attempting to..."
	text		"#str_380142"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_22_10_1
{
	description	"Eagle 10 making our run on the Networking Tower. Damn. The air defenses are strong."
	text		"#str_380143"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_22_10_2
{
	description	"I'm hit! I have to abort."
	text		"#str_380144"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_22_40_1
{
	description	"Aaaaaaaah! Aaaaaaaaaaaaaaah!"
	text		"#str_380145"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_22_40_2
{
	description	"Shit. Get a medic up here ASAP! We were trying to demo a door and the charge misfired. Lt.Leonard was hurt."
	text		"#str_380146"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_22_40_3
{
	description	"A medic has been dispatched."
	text		"#str_380147"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_22_50_1
{
	description	"Do something!"
	text		"#str_380148"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_22_50_2
{
	description	"It's too late. He's dead."
	text		"#str_380149"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_22_50_3
{
	description	"No, damn it. No."
	text		"#str_380150"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_22_50_4
{
	description	"Sorry, I did what I could. But I'm not a medic."
	text		"#str_380151"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_22_70_1
{
	description	"No time for grieving. Looks like we've got a fight on our hands."
	text		"#str_380152"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_24_10_1
{
	description	"Corporal Kane, I have bypassed security for the floor you are on. Take the door that is now opening."
	text		"#str_380153"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_24_20_1
{
	description	"We don't dare risk landing pods on the roof until the anti-aircraft guns are taken out."
	text		"#str_380154"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_24_30_1
{
	description	"Preparing to make a bombing run on the air defenses."
	text		"#str_380155"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_24_30_2
{
	description	"Roger that. I'm following you in."
	text		"#str_380156"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_24_30_3
{
	description	"I can barely see the target through all the..."
	text		"#str_380157"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_24_30_4
{
	description	"Eagle 12's been hit!"
	text		"#str_380158"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_24_40_1
{
	description	"Corporal Kane, leave one of your squad in the control room you're passing now."
	text		"#str_380159"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_24_42_1
{
	description	"Radar shows something large headed this way."
	text		"#str_380160"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_24_44_1
{
	description	"We have a visual. The Guardian creature is headed our way. Damn is it fast."
	text		"#str_380161"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_24_50_1
{
	description	"Kane, use the teleporter in front of you now. It will take you to the floor directly below the rooftop. There, you will have access to the security  station."
	text		"#str_380162"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_32_30_1
{
	description	"The Guardian has landed on the side of the tower."
	text		"#str_380163"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_34_10_1
{
	description	"Ah, the Core security station is finally deactivated. I won't bother asking what took you so long. Quickly make your way to the Core Teleporter."
	text		"#str_380164"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_34_20_3
{
	description	"HQ, we have a Marine down at the Core teleporter."
	text		"#str_380165"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_34_20_4
{
	description	"Perhaps he should have listened to me rather than trying to play the hero."
	text		"#str_380166"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_34_20_5
{
	description	"He just wanted to get in there and battle the Strogg."
	text		"#str_380167"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_34_20_6
{
	description	"That proved to be a mistake, didn't it?"
	text		"#str_380168"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_34_20_7
{
	description	"Kane, ignore the unfortunate soul laying dead on the ground. Because of your Strogg physiology you will be able to use the teleporter. Go now, it is the only way into the Core, and that houses the Nexus."
	text		"#str_380169"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_34_30_1
{
	description	"Corporal Kane, why do you hesitate to use the teleporter? Trust me when I say it is completely safe for you."
	text		"#str_380170"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_34_30_2
{
	description	"Please, Corporal - use the teleporter. Men are dying as you hesitate to enter the Core."
	text		"#str_380171"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_34_30_3
{
	description	"Corporal Kane, it is imperative you use the teleporter now. The Nexus must be destroyed."
	text		"#str_380172"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_14_10_1
{
	description	"Kane, this is Morris. Data Processing Tower's shut down. Looks like the Strogg are trying to stop us from reaching the core. You'll have to find  a way to bring it back online. Sledge is on his way. He should rendezvous with you shortly. Good luck. Morris out."
	text		"#str_380173"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_14_20_1
{
	description	"Good job, Kane. The building's back online."
	text		"#str_380174"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_14_30_1
{
	description	"Kane, this is Morris. Sledge just arrived at the Processing Tower. Hook up with him as soon as you can."
	text		"#str_380175"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_14_60_1
{
	description	"Gentlemen, Strauss's finally arrived at the Data Networking Tower. Your mission is gonna become more technical so I'm handing over communications to him. Good luck, guys. Get this mission done. Morris out."
	text		"#str_380176"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_14_6_1
{
	description	"Cortez, this is Morris. Are you and Kane at the Processing Tower yet?"
	text		"#str_380177"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_14_6_3
{
	description	"Okay, drop off Kane. You're needed at the Networking Tower right away. Another tramcar will be sent for Kane once he's taken care of the security station at the top of the Processing Tower."
	text		"#str_380178"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_14_6_5
{
	description	"No can do, Alex. Sledge will be here soon enough to lend Kane a hand."
	text		"#str_380179"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_14_70_1
{
	description	"Greetings, Corporals, this is Strauss. I have finally being to hack into the Nexus. Soon I will know all there is to know about the tower you are in."
	text		"#str_380180"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_14_80_1
{
	description	"The large machines in the area you have just entered are data pumps. They move information from the Networking Tower to the Storage Tower. This is a vital area to the Strogg so expect to meet strong resistance."
	text		"#str_380181"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_14_110_2
{
	description	"They are information routers... but they appear to be out of alignment. Kane should be able use the consoles to correct this problem."
	text		"#str_380182"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_14_110_3
{
	description	"That data stream you see will act as a guide. Once it�s path is corrected, the stream will lead you to the top floors of the processing tower."
	text		"#str_380183"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_14_135_3
{
	description	"We�re almost to the Processing Tower but we�ve been intercepted by a squadron of fliers!"
	text		"#str_380184"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_14_140_1
{
	description	"Maybe, mayday! My pod�s been hit! I�m going down! I�m going down!!"
	text		"#str_380185"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_14_140_6
{
	description	"Navigation�s out . . . . propulsion�s damaged. I�m coming in like a rock!"
	text		"#str_380186"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_14_175_2
{
	description	"There is nothing I can do for you in that section. Kane will have to find a solution."
	text		"#str_380187"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_15_50_1
{
	description	"The Core security interlock from the Processing Tower is now active. Well done, Corporal Kane. Sergeant Slidjonovitch, I would ask you to remain there and not allow the Strogg to reset that console."
	text		"#str_380188"
}

lipSync vo_3_1_15_50_3
{
	description	"Kane, you must now take the elevator down to the tram station and then take a tram to the Data Networking tower. I will meet you there. Strauss, out."
	text		"#str_380189"
}

lipSync vo_2_2_4_120_1
{
	description	"You're in the sterilization control room. There should be a way to turn on the system."
	text		"#str_380190"
}

lipSync vo_2_2_4_125_1
{
	description	"Hey! You did it! The sterilization system is online."
	text		"#str_380191"
}

lipSync vo_2_2_4_90_1
{
	description	"Great. Looks like the whole system needs to be rebooted. You're gonna have to locate and restart both the sterilization and assembly subsystems."
	text		"#str_380192"
}

